Charge and Bail bụ ihe nkiri na- atọ ọchị  Naịjirịa nke Uyoyou Adia duziri ma Eku Edewor na Matilda Ogunleye rụpụtara ya
Ihe nkiri a bụ Zainab Balogun na Stan Nze, Femi Adebayo, Folu Storms, Tope Olowoniyan, na Eso Dike na-akwado ọrụ
Ihe nkiri a na-akọ akụkọ Boma, onye ọkaiwu sitere na klaasị elu chọtara onwe ya n'ụlọ ọrụ na-ahụ maka ebubo na ịgbapụta n'oge afọ NYSC ya
Emere ihe nkiri a ka ewepụta ya na Ọktoba 21, 2021
